00:11:58.093 --> 00:11:59.928 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIKAWA] She's more
like a mascot than anything.

00:11:59.969 --> 00:12:01.471 position:50% align:center
Wait! So what you're saying is,

00:12:01.513 --> 00:12:03.807 position:50% align:center
