What's this about?

00:13:51.998 --> 00:13:54.125 position:50% align:center
Miyamura!
Thank goodness you're here!

00:13:54.167 --> 00:13:56.086 position:50% align:center
Please help! It's Hori.

00:13:56.127 --> 00:13:57.170 position:50% align:center
What's Hori?

00:13:57.212 --> 00:13:58.463 position:50% align:center
[ISHIKAWA] The student
council's giving her flack

00:13:58.505 --> 00:13:59.756 position:50% align:center
for some reason.

00:14:00.924 --> 00:14:03.134 position:50% align:center
