she didn't see it there.

00:14:11.810 --> 00:14:13.061 position:50% align:center
Did you double check,

00:14:13.103 --> 00:14:15.105 position:50% align:center
or is there a chance
you could be mistaken?

00:14:15.146 --> 00:14:17.023 position:50% align:center
Well, either way,
you guys are...

00:14:17.065 --> 00:14:17.982 position:50% align:center
[SENGOKU]
...still at fault.

00:14:18.024 --> 00:14:19.401 position:50% align:center
And, of course,
you have a point.

00:14:19.442 --> 00:14:21.778 position:50% align:center
That is, if the
missing budget report

00:14:21.820 --> 00:14:23.488 position:50% align:center
was actually in that pile.

00:14:23.530 --> 00:14:26.282 position:50% align:center
You have no one to blame
but yourself otherwise.

00:14:26.324 --> 00:14:27.283 position:50% align:center
So tell me,

00:14:27.325 --> 00:14:28.868 position:50% align:center
do you know for
certain it was there?

00:14:28.910 --> 00:14:30.954 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:14:31.413 --> 00:14:34.791 position:50% align:center
[HORI]
Yes, I do.

00:14:34.833 --> 00:14:36.251 position:50% align:center
But to be honest,

00:14:36.292 --> 00:14:38.545 position:50% align:center
I was so tired,
I can't remember.

00:14:38.586 --> 00:14:40.296 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT A]
Wow. Hori screwed up.

00:14:40.338 --> 00:14:41.673 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT I]
Isn't she in Class 1?

00:14:41.715 --> 00:14:42.924 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT B]
So how far behind are they,

00:14:42.966 --> 00:14:45.260 position:50% align:center
