00:14:45.301 --> 00:14:46.261 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT A]
I don't know.

00:14:46.302 --> 00:14:48.972 position:50% align:center
But I feel super sorry
for the president.

00:14:49.014 --> 00:14:50.640 position:50% align:center
So if this is
in fact your fault,

00:14:50.682 --> 00:14:52.434 position:50% align:center
all I want is an
apology from you.

00:14:52.475 --> 00:14:53.935 position:50% align:center
Is that so hard?

00:14:55.270 --> 00:14:56.980 position:50% align:center
Shut it, asshole!

00:14:57.022 --> 00:14:58.857 position:50% align:center
You're only making things worse!

00:14:58.898 --> 00:15:00.025 position:50% align:center
Leave her alone!

00:15:00.066 --> 00:15:01.735 position:50% align:center
Hori finished
that budget report!

00:15:01.776 --> 00:15:03.737 position:50% align:center
I know because I saw her do it!

00:15:03.778 --> 00:15:06.156 position:50% align:center
I also saw her turning it in!

00:15:08.199 --> 00:15:10.118 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT C] All she has
to do is apologize to him.

00:15:10.160 --> 00:15:11.161 position:50% align:center
What's the big deal?

00:15:11.202 --> 00:15:14.039 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT D] Three syllables
should not be this hard to say.

00:15:14.831 --> 00:15:15.707 position:50% align:center
[MIYAMURA]
Ishikawa.

00:15:15.749 --> 00:15:16.833 position:50% align:center
Gonna hold me back, too?

00:15:16.875 --> 00:15:19.461 position:50% align:center
