00:15:21.379 --> 00:15:24.632 position:50% align:center
Go ahead. It's your move.

00:15:28.678 --> 00:15:29.387 position:50% align:center
I...

00:15:29.429 --> 00:15:31.639 position:50% align:center
[MIYAMURA]
