00:15:39.647 --> 00:15:41.441 position:50% align:center
And what do you want?

00:15:41.483 --> 00:15:42.901 position:50% align:center
[MIYAMURA]
Mister President.

00:15:47.280 --> 00:15:50.825 position:50% align:center
[shocked screams]

00:15:50.867 --> 00:15:52.535 position:50% align:center
What the hell do you
think you're doing?

00:15:52.577 --> 00:15:54.954 position:50% align:center
Aw! My poor Sengoku!

00:15:54.996 --> 00:15:57.791 position:50% align:center
Just so you know,
violence is unacceptable!

00:15:57.832 --> 00:15:59.292 position:50% align:center
What possessed you
to do such a--

00:15:59.334 --> 00:16:00.543 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:16:00.585 --> 00:16:02.921 position:50% align:center
Is this the report
that went missing?

00:16:02.962 --> 00:16:04.798 position:50% align:center
[KONO]
Yeah. That's the one.

00:16:04.839 --> 00:16:06.299 position:50% align:center
But why do you have it?

00:16:06.341 --> 00:16:09.094 position:50% align:center
[MIYAMURA] It was left
behind in the hall yesterday.

00:16:09.135 --> 00:16:12.013 position:50% align:center
Ayasaki said I should trash it
because it wasn't important.

00:16:12.055 --> 00:16:14.224 position:50% align:center
Remi said no such thing! Oh!

00:16:22.232 --> 00:16:26.194 position:50% align:center
Oh... Guess that did happen.

00:16:28.071 --> 00:16:32.701 position:50% align:center
Reeeemiiii...

00:16:37.163 --> 00:16:40.709 position:50% align:center
You guys! I am so sorry!

00:16:40.750 --> 00:16:43.420 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT E] So they accused Hori
even though she didn't do it.

00:16:43.461 --> 00:16:45.171 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT F]
What even happened?

00:16:45.213 --> 00:16:46.506 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT G]
Who knows?

00:16:59.561 --> 00:17:02.605 position:50% align:center
[HORI] All's well that
ends well, as they say.

00:17:02.647 --> 00:17:06.026 position:50% align:center
