00:17:50.153 --> 00:17:53.073 position:50% align:center
So it's just one
childhood pal helping another.

00:17:53.114 --> 00:17:53.865 position:50% align:center
Heh.

00:17:53.907 --> 00:17:54.908 position:50% align:center
