the dude she turned down?

00:19:53.610 --> 00:19:55.195 position:50% align:center
[MIYAMURA] What about
something for her desk?

00:19:55.236 --> 00:19:55.987 position:50% align:center
[ISHIKAWA]
I thought if anyone knew

00:19:56.029 --> 00:19:58.073 position:50% align:center
what kind of stuff she likes,
it would be you!

00:19:58.114 --> 00:19:59.282 position:50% align:center
[MIYAMURA]
Umm...

00:20:01.117 --> 00:20:03.495 position:50% align:center
