and visit every single day?

00:20:23.139 --> 00:20:25.392 position:50% align:center
I don't think
he'll come here every day.

00:20:25.433 --> 00:20:27.560 position:50% align:center
Just keep in mind
that eventually

00:20:27.602 --> 00:20:29.813 position:50% align:center
