00:20:33.400 --> 00:20:35.110 position:50% align:center
When you graduate high school?

00:20:38.071 --> 00:20:41.741 position:50% align:center
[HORI] When will Miyamura
stop coming to my house?

00:20:41.783 --> 00:20:43.201 position:50% align:center
I don't know.

00:20:43.243 --> 00:20:46.204 position:50% align:center
